Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the whole federal government than riding first class in airplanes from...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最惬意的工作 莫过于坐在头等舱里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I'm sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you can trust me. I'm fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 你可以信任我 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't hear you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？我听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, you got a light?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 有火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir. Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir. You got a light?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下 你有火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your attention, please?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where you off to?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你到哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you headed?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要去哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to Amsterdam.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要去阿姆斯特丹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your attention, please?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The white zone is for the immediate loading\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}白色区域只允许马上登机的旅客通过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unloading of passengers only.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或刚下机的旅客通过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, sir. Enjoy your flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给 先生 祝你一路愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone and their mother's in the game right now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有人现在都在关心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got Korean phones, Japanese phones, Scandinavian phones.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么韩国手机 日本手机 斯堪的纳维亚手机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OS is trying to keep up with the hardware from 15 different manufacturers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}操作系统还得跟上15个不同厂家的硬件更新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been saying. No one listens to me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直就是这个意思 没人听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you're preaching to the choir! It makes absolutely no sense.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哥们 你这是班门弄斧了 完全不必跟我说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess I'm in your way.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没搞错？看来我挡了你的路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Yorkers, man, I swear to God. Give me two minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些纽约人啊 给我两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way, sir. Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请这里来 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. Listen to me. I cannot stay in London for three days.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听我说 我不能在伦敦停留3天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me on the next flight back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给我安排最快的航班回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, look. This is...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 听我说 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bad time for...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在时间不合适…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You have to do what you have to do." Well, guess what? So do I.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"你是不得已的" 你猜怎么着？我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long flights are the worst.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}长途飞行是最糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, baby.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗨 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, passengers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚上好 乘客们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mix-up with my reservation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的预订出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to have a window seat and they put me in an aisle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我本该是靠窗的座位 他们却给我安排了靠过道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could move some people around,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也许你可以调调座位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'cause I was guaranteed the window seat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为我订的是靠窗座位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that, Ms. Summers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起了 萨默斯太太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time we are inviting passengers with small children,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们请带孩子的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or who require assistance, to board at this time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是需要协助的乘客 此时登机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, in the boarding area,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}重复一遍 在登机区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we are ready to begin our priority boarding Flight 10 to London.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞往伦敦的10次航班开始优先乘客登机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin general boarding in just a few minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}几分钟后将开始普通乘客登机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all set to board?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们都准备好登机了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to go on the runway?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们必须去跑道上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sweetheart. Is this everything?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来 孩子 行李都在里面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My mom checked my big bag for me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我妈妈为我检查了大包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you flown by yourself before?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以前自己坐过飞机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is my first time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有 这是我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna have a lovely time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会过得很愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome aboard. Yes, just through there and down to the left.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎登机 只需要穿过这里 然后左拐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, this is Becca. It's her first time on an airplane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 这是贝嘉 这是她第一次坐飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful. Who's waiting for you in London?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好 谁在伦敦等你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've a seat by the window all picked out for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们已经为你选择了靠窗座位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know it may seem scary, but flying's really quite fun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道看起来很可怕 但是飞行是很有乐趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this little guy made a run for it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这个小家伙逃走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亨利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he looks like a Henry. That's a good name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他长相适合这名字 是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well... - Becca.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 那么… - 贝嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becca, I think Henry's a little scared.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}贝嘉 我觉得亨利有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can show him how it's done.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也许你能为他做个榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, am I in your way?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 我挡了你的路？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}又一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are right up here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚上好 各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reminder, all carry-on luggage must fit in the overhead bin\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在此提醒 所有手提行李必须塞在舱顶行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or be safely stowed under the seat in front of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是安全的塞在您面前的座位下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're having trouble fitting your luggage,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果行李塞不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be happy to check it for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们愿帮您寄存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for choosing British Aqualantic. Enjoy the flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢您选择英国亚奎兰蒂航空公司航班 祝旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, is there somebody sitting there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请问这个座位有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you know who has that seat? - No, sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 这是谁的座位？- 不知道 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is somebody sitting here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm on the plane. And guess what? They effed up my reservation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 我在飞机上 你猜怎么着？他们搞错了我的预订
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We land at 7:35. Did they book a car?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}7:35抵达 他们预订汽车了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. Hang on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Sir? I'm here in 3B.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下 先生 我的座位号是3B
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if maybe you'd switch seats\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请问能不能和你换下座位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with me so I could have the window?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我好靠窗坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you care?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you speak English?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会说英语吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Excuse me. Sir?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. I'm right here, I'm in 3B\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 我的座位在这里 3B
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was just wondering if maybe you would prefer the aisle,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请问你是否更愿意坐在靠过道的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or if you don't care, if you would\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或者坐在哪里都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,switch with me for the window seat?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能不能和我换换座位？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people just sleep anyway, so I was wondering if...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很多人都是睡一路 我想问问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Why not?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 换就换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. I really appreciate that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}太谢谢了 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, let me get out of your way.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起 我先让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's room right up here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里有地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqualantic is pleased to offer extensive in-flight entertainment\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚奎兰蒂航空公司愿意提供广泛的机上娱乐节目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with hundreds of video and music programming at your fingertips.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以方便的订阅数百份影视和音乐节目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Are you there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What? - Hello?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么？- 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Your phone. - Oh, shit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你的手机 - 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello? - Hi. Hi, hi.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 喂？- 嗨 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you when we land, okay? All right, bye.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我下飞机再联系你 好吗？再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rough day, huh?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今天不顺心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you have no idea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get a gin and tonic, when you get a chance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}方便的话 给我拿杯奎宁杜松子酒可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Of course. - Make that two, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 好的 - 我也要一杯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nancy, right? Gwen. - Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你叫南希 对吧？我叫格温 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God for you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感谢上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl doesn't show up and leaves me\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她没来 只留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to handle two cabins. You're a lifesaver.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}服务两个客舱 你帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pass out, just promise to catch me before I hit the floor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如我晕过去了 请务必在我摔倒前扶住我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I do first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非是我先晕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get you gentlemen anything before we taxi?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}起飞前你们还需要什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks, Nance, I'm fine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用了 南希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ground, this is AQ-10, we're ready to disconnect ground power.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}控制塔 我是AQ-10次航班 准备断开地面电源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You naughty boy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naughty.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you order gin and tonic?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不是点了奎宁杜松子酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause she brought you a water.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她给你拿了矿泉水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my lucky day.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今天我不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, ladies and gentlemen,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}晚上好 各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,welcome aboard British Aqualantic Flight 10, non-stop service to London.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎乘坐英国亚奎兰蒂航空公司10次航班 直达伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your captain, David McMillan,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是机长大卫·麦克米伦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,flying with First Officer Kyle Rice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和副驾驶员凯尔·赖斯一起驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we expect a smooth ride this evening\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}预计今夜一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- with a flight time of just over six hours. - Seatbelts, thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 飞行时间约6小时多 - 请系好安全带 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have you in the air momentarily.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们很快就将起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a beautiful picture they took of her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她的这张照片很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, could you move your seat-back forward? Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 能否把靠背向前的？谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight attendants, please be seated for takeoff.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}乘务人员 请坐好准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that for? Is that for luck?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何这么做 图个吉利？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that. My daughter gave it to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}差不多 是我女儿给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than a gin and tonic, I bet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肯定比奎宁杜松子酒强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jen.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我叫珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我叫比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You fly much? - All the time, actually.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你乘飞机次数多吗？- 经常乘飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can tell.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the takeoff. Once we're in the air, I'll...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是起飞时紧张 等升空之后 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have a seizure?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就癫痫发作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I promise.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没事的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually fly all the time?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真的经常乘飞机？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things you never get used to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有些事情永远习惯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old's your daughter?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你女儿多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, she's, uh, 17.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如今17岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olivia.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's nice. - Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 不错 - 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that name, it's a nice name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜欢这名字 是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Why'd she give you the ribbon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她为何给你这个丝带？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kids have blankets, stuffed animals. Olivia had ribbons.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有些小孩子喜欢毛毯 动物玩具 奥利维亚喜欢丝带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was hers when she was little.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在她小时候 这曾是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd tie it to a finger or toe before going to bed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她睡觉前常把它绑在手指或脚趾上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then in the morning, she'd make me guess.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}第二天早上醒来 她会让我猜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where she put it? - Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 猜绑在哪里？- 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute. That's really cute.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真可爱 好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and then she grew up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 然后她长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I need it more than she did.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能我比她更需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyway\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you do for a living?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是什么做职业的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fly a lot.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我经常出差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. yeah?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I think that\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 不过我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try to get some sleep.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想睡上一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get some sleep, sure. - Yeah, it's gonna be a long flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 睡一觉 当然 - 是啊 这一路很长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah. Sleep well.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 睡个好觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop! - Baby...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 放手 - 宝贝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're crazy! - You're so hot, baby, I can't stop it! I can't!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你疯了 - 你这么美 我控制不住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are watching!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别人看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. Nobody's watching. Nobody.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of my mom, with no pants on\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当着我妈的面 他没穿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and half a Toblerone in his mouth.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘴里还含着半块巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你认识他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tea do you have?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们有什么样的茶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have chamomile. Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要甘菊茶 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This your idea of a joke? - What're you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 有你这么开玩笑的吗？- 你胡说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem with me, say it to my face.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果对我有意见 当着我的面说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play games on a flight in a secure network.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要在飞机上 在保安网络中玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to calm down, partner.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你冷静 拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a cop for 25 years. I knew men like you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我当了25年警察 我了解你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men like me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我这种人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men like me follow goddamn protocol.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我这样的人循规蹈矩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not even supposed to be talking right now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们现在不该交谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secure network, Jack!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是保安网络 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, what the hell are you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 你到底在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't deny you sent these.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要否认是你发送的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, I didn't send these.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 不是我发送的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someone on this flight is threatening to kill a passenger\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么飞机上有人威胁杀一名乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless $150 million is transferred in the next 18 minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非在18分钟内转账1.5亿美元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows about this?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁知道这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say no way. It's bullshit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看不可能 这是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any threat to an aircraft requires immediate landing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}任何对飞机的威胁都要紧急降落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, yeah, all right. If there is a threat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 假如有威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Bill. You wanna be the agent\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 比尔 难道你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who lands an international flight\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让国际航班迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because some asshole knows your personal problems?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就因为某个混蛋知道你的个人缺点？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sends you a couple of joke texts?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给你发几个笑话短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, I gotta ask you, how many have you had today?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 我得问你 你今天喝了多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A threat's a threat!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}威胁都要认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really need to think this through, partner, all right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要把这事考虑清楚 拍档 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, how do you kill somebody aboard\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么可能在飞机上杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a crowded plane and get away with it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}又能逃之夭夭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty hard to pull that off, don't you think?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很难办到这一点 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, if there's not a situation, you don't create one.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果没有情况 你就不要制造情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see the captain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我去找机长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep your eye on the main cabin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你盯着主舱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill? Don't panic the cockpit. Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 不要让驾驶舱惊慌 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, it's five hours in\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的 过了5个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, out of nowhere, he suddenly sits up and he says...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后突然之间 他就站起来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How do we validate the threat? - We can't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们如何核实这一威胁呢？- 核实不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? TSA says a full cross check on the passenger manifest\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长 运输安全局说 全面调查登机乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could take 25 to 30 minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能需要25-30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can divert the flight, if this is for real.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如确有其事 我们可以改换航线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nearest airport?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最近的机场在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's 95 minutes back to Halifax,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已经离开哈利法克斯95分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two hours to Iceland, three to London.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}距冰岛两小时 伦敦三小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're midway over the Atlantic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们正在大西洋中间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this juice fast I'm on. Gives me the shakes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正在节食 手经常发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your call, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}决定权在你 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a situation?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这算是威胁情况吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we review the footage?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能看一下录像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's recorded directly to the black box.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是录制在黑匣子中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can watch all the camera feeds live from the galley?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在餐间可以看实时监控吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back on the line with TSA.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}继续和运输安全局联系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See if they can back trace this account number.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看他们能否追踪这一账号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, I'll need the passenger manifest.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在此期间 我也需要乘客名单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see if I can find him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看能不能找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in 10 minutes, I'd like you to switch off the network system.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但10分钟后 我要你切断网络
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want him checking to see if a transfer's been made.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们不能让他查看是否已经转账
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, come with me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two cameras in business, six in coach.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}商务舱有两个摄像头 经济舱有6个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna need more eyes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们还需要人监控
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get another attendant.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我再找个乘务员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:22:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How well do you know the crew?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你对乘务人员有多熟悉？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very well.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me. - Yeah?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 打扰一下 - 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me, please?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to come right now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要我现在就去？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bad idea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was sitting beside me when this started.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这事开始的时候 她就坐在我旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only two people I trust on this airplane are you and her.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这飞机上我唯一信任的就是你和她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me with what? What's going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}信任我什么？出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I text, you circle any passenger with a phone\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我发短信 你们圈出拿手机的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or acting like they have a phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或像是拿着手机的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I understand what it is you want me to do...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不明白你要我干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just do as I ask.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 就按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, looks like\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客 看来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.38,0:24:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've hit some unexpected turbulence.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们遇到一些意外的气流
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to your seats and keep your seatbelts fastened\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请回到各自座位上 系上安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until it's safe to move about the cabin. Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}直到在机舱内可以安全走动 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.87,0:25:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. 9B.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那里 9B
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.42,0:25:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seat 9B. David Norton.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}座位号9B 大卫·诺顿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.28,0:25:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22C.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}22C座位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Austin Reilly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥斯汀·雷利
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.17,0:25:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2F.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}2F座位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.13,0:25:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jason Cole.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}詹森·科尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14C.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}14C座位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.14,0:26:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14C, Charles Wheeler.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}14C 查尔斯·维勒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13B.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}13B座位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.65,0:26:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fahim Nasir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}法西姆·纳西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.61,0:26:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5B.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}5B座位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.69,0:26:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5B. Iris Marianne.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}5B座位 爱丽丝·玛丽安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.49,0:26:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better answer it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你该接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.70,0:26:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.70,0:26:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.55,0:26:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who is this? - This is Philip Marenick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你是谁？- 菲利普·麦尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with TSA. I understand from the captain you have a situation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}运输安全局的 我听机长说你遇到情况
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.89,0:26:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to speak to my supervisor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要和我的上级谈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'm calling from the DHS here in D.C.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是在华盛顿的国土安全部打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.35,0:26:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, I am your supervisor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从现在起 我就是你的上级
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.52,0:26:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Agent Marks, I need you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工 我需要你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.60,0:26:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to run seat numbers by you. I need red flags and priors.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要你调查几个座位号 告诉我危险人物和可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.52,0:26:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's a very serious request you put in. - 20G.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你这个要求很严肃 - 20G座位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Marks, I need you to take me\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工 我要你跟我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.82,0:26:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the events from the beginning.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}讲讲整个事情经过
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.03,0:26:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're looking into tracing the account number you gave us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们正调查你给我们的账号
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.99,0:26:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20G again.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}又是20G
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.07,0:26:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as you know, protocol dictates in these situations...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 在这种情况下 按规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.95,0:27:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we corroborate everything with the second officer on board.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要和机上第二空警核实
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.91,0:27:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20G again.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还是20G
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.99,0:27:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.04,0:27:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not who? Look, I'd rather not jump to any conclusions.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是谁？听着 我宁愿不要急于下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.37,0:27:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Bill, I don't think you're in a position to sort out\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 你目前不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.54,0:27:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's a suspect or not at this point.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}判断谁是嫌疑犯 谁不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.17,0:27:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.34,0:27:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Marks, I need some sort of acknowledgment from you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工 我需要你表示服从
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.06,0:27:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks, you need to answer me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯 你要回复我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.43,0:27:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.65,0:27:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks, are you there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your seat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回到你的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.62,0:27:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son-of-a-bitch!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.00,0:27:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.17,0:27:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hand it over! - What're you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 交出来 - 你说什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.79,0:27:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, look at me, okay? I need this money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 看着我 我需要这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.59,0:27:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cut you in...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以分给你一份…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.63,0:27:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give me the goddamn phone, Jack. - Just listen to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 给我手机 杰克 - 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the phone...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给我手机…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.35,0:28:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack! You son-of-a-bitch.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杰克 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.19,0:28:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give it up, Marks. - Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 放手 马克斯 - 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.60,0:28:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give it up. - Stop it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 放手 - 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Jack!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.61,0:28:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.03,0:28:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.17,0:28:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Jack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别这么做 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.73,0:28:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:28:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.73,0:29:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.86,0:29:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Jack!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别这么做 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.73,0:31:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, this is your captain speaking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客 我是机长
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.86,0:31:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the inconvenience...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我为带来的不便表示歉意…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.27,0:31:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.61,0:31:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our network is down for the moment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们目前网络中断
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.28,0:31:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just bear with us, we'll attempt to restart the Internet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请稍等一下 我们会试图重启网络
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Turn the network back on. - What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 恢复网络 - 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The network, turn it on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打开网络
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep you posted.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们会继续通知你们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the network system back on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要重启网络
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.29,0:31:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Nance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你去吧 南希
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.97,0:31:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The account number you gave us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你给我们的账号
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.51,0:31:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是在你的名下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.64,0:31:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.01,0:31:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TSA just confirmed it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}运输安全局刚核实了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.39,0:31:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.06,0:31:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know me. You know I'd never do...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你了解我 你知道我绝不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.86,0:31:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.32,0:31:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the 20 minutes are up. Has anything happened?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}20分钟时间已到 出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.45,0:31:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.12,0:31:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a hoax.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能只是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.83,0:32:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some elaborate middle finger to the airline industry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对航空公司发泄不满
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.58,0:32:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Are you waiting?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下 你在等着进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.84,0:32:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Go ahead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.67,0:32:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特工…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.92,0:32:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, ma'am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.18,0:32:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Marenick, who you spoke with,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和你通过电话的麦尼克特工
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.34,0:32:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will continue to handle the investigation from D.C.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}会在华盛顿继续调查
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.43,0:32:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,David...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.52,0:32:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they've asked me to take your badge and your gun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们也让我收走你的警徽和手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.69,0:32:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No. - Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 不 - 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.86,0:32:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No. - Bill...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 不 - 比尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.44,0:32:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the air marshal.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是空警
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.78,0:32:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bill... - Okay. Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 比尔… - 好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just sit back, relax,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你去坐下 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.70,0:32:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- and... - Enjoy the flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 然后… - 享受旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the flight, yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对 享受旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.56,0:33:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it him? The guy in 20G?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是他吗？20G座位上的那人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.39,0:33:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was nothing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.48,0:33:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my stupid phone in the sink.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不小心把手机掉在水池里了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.73,0:33:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, I do that all the time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天 我也经常这样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.69,0:33:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost like five phones in six months,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}半年里损失了5部手机
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.03,0:33:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I learned this little trick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后我学会一个小窍门
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, should I be worried?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我还需要担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.03,0:33:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 完全不必
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.45,0:33:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to involve you, I'm sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不该把你卷入进来 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.87,0:33:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if it's not him, then why do you have his phone?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}既然不是他 为何他的手机在你手上？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be careful, even when\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了万无一失 即便
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing to be concerned about.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.75,0:33:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.79,0:33:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a passenger, don't I have the right to know what's going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}身为乘客 我不是有权知道发生什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.55,0:33:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Listen... Jen, right? - Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 听我说… 你叫珍妮 是吧？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.26,0:33:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an innocent prank. Some kid with a cell phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是个恶作剧 某个拿手机的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was on the ground, I'd catch him\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如是在地面上 我立刻就能
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.93,0:33:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in two seconds flat, but up here,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抓住他 但在飞机上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.72,0:33:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,traveling at 500 miles an hour, I can't track his phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}500英里的时速 我无法追踪他的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.10,0:33:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.19,0:33:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do? Aren't you an air marshal?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么办法？你不是空警吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.11,0:33:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, please return to your seat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女士 请回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.40,0:33:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me "ma'am"?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你叫我"女士"？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to your seat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.45,0:33:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Did you call me "ma'am"?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没搞错？你叫我"女士"？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.99,0:33:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.70,0:34:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我去就是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.37,0:34:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you. - Ugh.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 谢谢配合 - 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.20,0:35:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Hammond?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈蒙德特工
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.56,0:35:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.48,0:35:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. The indicator must be broken.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起 指示器肯定出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for Agent Hammond.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我本来是找哈蒙德特工
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.78,0:36:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.21,0:36:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, wait. Wait!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.71,0:36:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.26,0:36:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冷静 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.76,0:36:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I can explain this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 你听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.77,0:36:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a setup.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是个圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain just told me that the account\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长刚才告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they want the money wired to is in my name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们要求的账号是在我的名下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.61,0:36:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I would extort $150 million\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难道我会用我名下的账户
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using an account in my own name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}敲诈1.5亿美元？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.49,0:36:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was transporting cocaine, Nancy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他在走私可卡因 南希
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever we're looking for knew that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们调查的人知道这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He threatened Hammond, made him paranoid.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他威胁哈蒙德 让他心神不定
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.12,0:36:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out, and Hammond tried to kill me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我发现之后 哈蒙德想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.42,0:36:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who's doing this, he wants it to look like this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}做这件事的人 希望造成这种假象
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like two federal agents are the ones doing this, not him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好像这事是两个联邦特工干的 而不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.93,0:37:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack pulled a gun on me. I had no choice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杰克拿枪对着我 我没别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.10,0:37:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.35,0:37:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.94,0:37:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I could never do something like this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道我绝不会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.49,0:37:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.50,0:37:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to believe me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.17,0:37:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 13 minutes, someone else will die, unless I find him first.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}13分钟后 还有人会死 除非我先找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.43,0:37:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to help me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.02,0:37:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, may I have your attention, please?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Bill Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我叫比尔·马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.52,0:38:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the federal air marshal assigned to this flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是驻本航班的空警
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.36,0:38:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the disturbance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.65,0:38:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The TSA has recently instituted a policy\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}运输安全局最近出台一项规定
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.99,0:38:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of random searches aboard international flights.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以随机搜查国际航班的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.53,0:38:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this is one of three lucky flights this month.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}遗憾的是 这是本月中的三次航班之一
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be coming through the cabin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我将穿过机舱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.37,0:38:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I call your name and seat number,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我喊到你的名字和座位号
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.29,0:38:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please stand up and move into the aisle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请站起来 走到过道上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.17,0:38:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in possession of an illegal substance, item or weapon,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你持有违禁品或武器
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.34,0:38:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's best to just step forward now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最好现在就站出来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.72,0:38:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, you might want to hear this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长 你来听听这个
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.51,0:38:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need everybody to place both hands on the seat in front of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要大家都把双手放在前面座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.89,0:38:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他妈的在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.72,0:38:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.14,0:38:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact TSA, tell them we have a possible hijacking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}联系运输安全局 告诉他们我们可能遭遇劫机
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.56,0:38:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nancy, what's going on? - It's just a random search.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 南希 怎么了？- 只是随机搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.57,0:38:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.45,0:38:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}借过
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.57,0:38:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer Summers?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}珍妮·萨默斯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.33,0:38:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have told you about the bomb in my bag?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要不要告诉你我包里的炸弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.41,0:38:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not use that word on a plane, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请不要在飞机上用这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.91,0:39:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I move on to the main cabin, you watch business class.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等我去了主舱之后 你盯着商务舱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.71,0:39:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see anything suspicious,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果看到任何可疑情况
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.21,0:39:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anything at all, get my attention.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}任何情况 就引起我的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.67,0:39:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Scream, if you have to. - Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 必要的话就喊叫 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.21,0:39:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,American paranoia.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国神经病
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.22,0:39:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iris Marianne, 5B. Stand up, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爱丽丝·玛丽安 座位号5B 请站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.89,0:39:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how older men pick up younger women?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}长者都是这么勾引年轻女子的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fondle first, talk later?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先摸一遍 然后再聊？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.43,0:39:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}手机
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.52,0:39:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you enter your number?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么不把你的号码输进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.23,0:39:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little young for me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你对我来说太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does this guy think he is?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这人以为自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.79,0:39:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Just calm down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没事的 你冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just married? - Yesterday.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 刚结婚？- 昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.75,0:39:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations. - Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 恭喜 - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.63,0:39:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.96,0:39:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to worry about. Happens all the time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么担心的 这是常事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 13B, Fahim Nasir. - Bullshit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 13B座位 法西姆·纳西尔 - 胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.05,0:39:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stand. - Thank you, sir.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 请起立 - 谢谢 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.06,0:40:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感觉还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.31,0:40:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying is not my cup of tea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞行不是我喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.31,0:40:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁说不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.56,0:40:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're a doctor. - How do you know?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你是个医生 - 你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.44,0:40:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bag. Can you fetch it up, please?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能把你的包拿上来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.57,0:40:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. It's right down here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的 就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.95,0:40:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of doctor?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哪个一科的医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Molecular neuroscience.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}分子神经科学
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.66,0:40:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感觉很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.00,0:40:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, man, some of us need to get some sleep.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂 我们有人还要睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.42,0:40:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, sit down. Be quiet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 坐下 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.17,0:40:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14C, Charles Wheeler? Stand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}14C 查尔斯·维勒？站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing in his bag?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他的包里什么也没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the purpose of your trip?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你此行目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.89,0:40:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a client in Brighton. I'm a bankruptcy attorney.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在英国有个当事人 我是破产律师
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.43,0:40:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You any good?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？水平高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.69,0:40:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why? Oh, you need one? - Sit down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 怎么 你需要个律师？- 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.77,0:40:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, you need to keep your hands on the seat in front of you. Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 你要把手放在前面座位上 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.82,0:40:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy. Are we next?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是荒唐 接下来搜查我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.70,0:41:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放松
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.21,0:41:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, 22C. Austin Reilly. Stand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 22C 奥斯汀·雷利 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.21,0:41:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look. Can we move this along? Seriously, man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能接着往前走吗？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.21,0:41:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna tell you again.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不会对你说第二遍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.51,0:41:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Reilly, what do you do for a living?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雷利先生 你是做什么职业的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.80,0:41:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NYPD.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}纽约警察局的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.72,0:41:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,London your final destination?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}伦敦是你的目的地？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.64,0:41:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fairy brother's getting married to a guy with a British accent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的宝贝弟弟要和一个英国口音的男人结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.73,0:41:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I take a look at your phone?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能看看你的手机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.40,0:41:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man. Are you serious'?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 没搞错？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some Big Brother-type shit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这也太欺负人了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.86,0:41:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your seat.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.07,0:41:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, step into the aisle. Come on, up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你 到过道上 快 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.08,0:41:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UP! Right now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马上站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.41,0:41:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, man, I'm good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.08,0:41:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking. Shades off.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}必须站起来 摘掉墨镜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.37,0:41:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. What is it, like 2:00 a.m.?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 现在有凌晨两点了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.83,0:41:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back up there so I can go back to sleep, man?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你还是回去 让我接着睡吧 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shades. - No, dude!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 墨镜 - 我不摘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man! Yo, chill!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我看看你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.43,0:41:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a phone, man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没手机
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.39,0:42:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't yours?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这不是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.97,0:42:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I ain't never seen that before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我从未见过它
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.43,0:42:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks a hell of a lot like the one you were using at the gate.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看起来很像你在登机口用过的那部
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.74,0:42:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.95,0:42:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.95,0:42:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.90,0:42:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Amsterdam?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不是去阿姆斯特丹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.65,0:42:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm connecting to London.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在伦敦有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.32,0:42:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your boarding pass. What's your name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我看看你的登机证 你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.94,0:42:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom Bowen. Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}汤姆·博文 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.20,0:43:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, take it easy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你轻点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.95,0:43:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.33,0:43:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.66,0:43:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I have rights!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有权利
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.00,0:43:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}过来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.71,0:43:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Marenick? - Marks, what the hell is going on there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 麦尼克？- 马克斯 你他妈在这干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.42,0:43:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. The threat is real.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听我说 威胁是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop doing whatever you're doing immediately.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要你立即停止你正在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.67,0:43:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a suspect in custody. I need a background check.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我拘捕了一个嫌疑犯 我需要背景调查
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.84,0:43:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seat 24E, Tom Bowen, B-O-W-E-N.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}座位号24E 汤姆·博文
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.84,0:43:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have unlawfully subdued innocent passengers, Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你非法制伏无辜乘客 马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.97,0:43:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没时间说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.02,0:43:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called your supervisor before the flight and threatened him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你登机前给你的上级打电话 还威胁了他
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.31,0:43:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What'? - He wouldn't book you an overtime flight\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么？- 他不肯为你安排航班
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.02,0:43:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you said you'd do what you had to do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就说要做不得已的事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.48,0:43:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I didn't threaten anyone. - Is that right? Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我没威胁任何人 - 是吗？马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.27,0:43:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to run a full check on Tom Bowen, seat 24E.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要对汤姆·博文的全面调查 座位号24E
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.36,0:43:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Marks, damn you! - Now! You're wasting time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 马克斯 真是的 - 快 别浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.49,0:43:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks... Agent Marks, you are hereby relieved of duty. Do you hear me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工 你现在被解除职责了 听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In three minutes, someone on this plane is gonna die. Do you hear me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}3分钟后 这架飞机上会死人 听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.87,0:43:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowen is clean, Bill. He's a schoolteacher, for Christ's sake.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}博文是干净的 他是个学校老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.45,0:43:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has family in London.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他在伦敦有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on that flight is clean. Everyone except you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机上的人都是干净的 只除了你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.30,0:43:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.84,0:44:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Amsterdam.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你说了阿姆斯特丹
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.14,0:44:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you where you were going.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我从未问你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.85,0:44:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You volunteered that information.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你主动提供这一信息
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.47,0:44:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you lie to a federal agent?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么要对联邦特工撒谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.18,0:44:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I didn't know you were a federal agent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我并不知道你是联邦特工
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.23,0:44:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you lie to a stranger?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么要对陌生人说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.52,0:44:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can answer questions now, or in federal custody when we land.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要么现在回答问题 要么降落后在联邦拘留所中回答
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.07,0:44:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Okay, Jesus.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.19,0:44:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd give me $100 if I asked you where you were flying. Okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他说只要我问你去哪里 就给我100块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.53,0:44:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I said Amsterdam.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知自己为啥要说阿姆斯特丹
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to God, I didn't know you were a federal marshal.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我对天发誓 并不知道你是空警
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.86,0:44:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bullshit! - I swear to God!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 胡说 - 我对天发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.41,0:44:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to play a prank on his friend. Will, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他说他想耍弄一个朋友 你叫威尔 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.20,0:44:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.79,0:44:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill. Whatever, man. I did it for 100 bucks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 都一样 我是为了100块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.37,0:44:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who was he? - I don't know!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 他是谁？- 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.42,0:44:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he look like?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他长什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.50,0:44:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was white with brown hair, a European accent, like 30, 35 years old...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}白人 褐色头发 欧洲口音 大约30-35岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.75,0:44:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is he on this plane? - I don't know, I didn't see him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 他在这飞机上吗？- 不知道 我没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.92,0:44:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went back, he didn't pay me, he was already gone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等我回来时 他没给我钱 他已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.01,0:44:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You'd know him if you saw him? - I don't know!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 看到他你能认出来吗？- 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.84,0:44:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw him get on the plane, man, I swear!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没看见他上这架飞机 我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.05,0:44:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humor me. Look!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帮我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.10,0:44:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.06,0:44:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, look.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.61,0:44:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.23,0:44:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.94,0:45:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come on, look! - God damn it! I don't see him!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 走 看看 - 该死的 我没看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.95,0:45:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right there. - Where?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 在那里 - 哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.28,0:45:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there. The glasses.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那里 那个戴眼镜的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.20,0:45:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, move.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}走
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.04,0:45:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.46,0:45:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You. Look at me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你 你 看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.46,0:45:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me! What's your name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看着我 你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.13,0:45:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael. Michael Tate.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}迈克 迈克·塔特
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.76,0:45:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well? - It's not him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 是不是？- 不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.59,0:45:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're sure? - Yeah, God damn it, I'm sure!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你确定？- 是的 该死的 我确定
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.06,0:45:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if I'd seen him get on the plane,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如我见过他上这架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.47,0:45:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've gone and asked him for my money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我肯定去向他要钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.81,0:45:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.60,0:45:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, watch business class.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 盯着商务舱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.57,0:45:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转过身
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.82,0:45:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you serious? - Don't talk.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你是认真的？- 别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.16,0:45:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, sit down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.79,0:45:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.38,0:46:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.54,0:46:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.52,0:47:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody remain in your seats.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有人留在各自座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.52,0:47:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, please remain in your seats\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客 请留在各自座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.57,0:47:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep your seatbelts fastened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}系上安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.91,0:47:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, please remain in your seats\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客 请留在各自座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.25,0:47:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep your seatbelts fastened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}系上安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.21,0:47:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, are you okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.96,0:47:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah. - You sure?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 没事 - 你确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.71,0:47:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.72,0:47:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started having chest pains, then he just collapsed over the yoke!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他开始胸痛 然后就倒在操纵杆上了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.23,0:47:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on! Wake up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.94,0:47:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sit down! - What the hell was that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 坐下 - 刚才怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.27,0:47:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's under control.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都在控制中
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.02,0:47:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.86,0:47:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the captain okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.94,0:47:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Dr. Nasir? - I didn't do anything, I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 纳西尔医生 - 我什么都没干…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.20,0:47:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}跟我来 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.03,0:47:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshal! Is someone gonna tell us what the hell is going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空警 告诉我 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.08,0:47:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.12,0:47:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! People are scared!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂 人们很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.12,0:48:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a right to know why you searched us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们有权知道你为何搜查我们
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this plane almost went down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何这架飞机差点坠毁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.96,0:48:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Marshal, you and I are gonna have a conversation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空警 咱俩要谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.21,0:48:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you walk away from me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别一走了之
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.96,0:48:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, cockpit, now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}医生 马上去驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.30,0:48:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting that guy in the cockpit?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你让这个人进驾驶舱？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.80,0:48:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what's gonna happen. You're gonna get back to your seat,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下面这么做 你回到你的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.89,0:48:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're gonna sit down, and you're gonna shut up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要坐下 然后闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.97,0:48:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}否则呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.01,0:48:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From one cop to another,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.31,0:48:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.74,0:48:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing I could do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.52,0:49:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, miss? You were sitting next to that guy, the marshal?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下 小姐 你坐在那个空警旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.53,0:49:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what's happening?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.03,0:49:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一点不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.66,0:49:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no evidence of assault.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有受到击打的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.04,0:49:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be poison. Induced anaphylaxis.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能是中毒 引发过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What? - Allergic reaction.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么？- 过敏性反应
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.29,0:49:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without an autopsy, I...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不解剖的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.55,0:49:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.63,0:49:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, would you mind seeing\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}医生 你能不能看看
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.88,0:49:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if any of the passengers in coach need medical assistance?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机舱内有没有乘客需要医疗救助？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.68,0:49:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.55,0:49:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This stays between us. Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要跟别人说 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.23,0:49:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, go with him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 跟他去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.08,0:50:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.58,0:50:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle, did the captain leave the cockpit since I last spoke with him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔 我和机长交谈之后 他离开过驾驶舱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.92,0:50:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You? - No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你呢？- 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.93,0:50:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else enter?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有人进来过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.39,0:50:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.72,0:50:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he had anything to eat or drink?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他吃过或喝过什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.10,0:50:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.06,0:50:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you or the captain had any reason to unlock this door?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你或者机长有任何原因打开这个门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.73,0:50:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然没有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.77,0:50:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you and he were both alone here,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么这20分钟时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.40,0:50:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the flight deck, for the past 20 minutes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你和他单独在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.94,0:50:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.11,0:50:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get emotional.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别动情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.20,0:50:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting emotional? Look at you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我动情绪？看看你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.99,0:50:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice, if you have a problem with me...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赖斯 假如你对我有意见…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.45,0:50:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a problem with my friend dying next to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有意见的是朋友死在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.12,0:50:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a problem with being accused\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有意见的是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.83,0:50:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of not only murder, but also hijacking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}被指控谋杀 还有劫机
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.50,0:50:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't accuse you of hijacking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没指控你劫机
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.91,0:50:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ, I've heard about you. About your problems with money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我听说了你的事 你的问题是缺钱
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.25,0:50:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With drinking. TSA.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有酗酒 运输安全局
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.09,0:50:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave a paranoid alcoholic a gun and a badge\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给一个疯子酒鬼发了一把枪和一个警徽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.80,0:50:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they put him on my plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还让他上了我的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.46,0:50:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.26,0:50:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna hit me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要打我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.97,0:51:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell... Hey! Hey! What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别告诉… 嘿 你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.89,0:51:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This door stays locked until this plane lands safely. Okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在飞机安全降落前 绝不要打开舱门 可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.99,0:51:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Marenick... - Marks, God damn it, I thought I told you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 麦尼克… - 马克斯 该死的 我不是告诉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.28,0:51:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长死了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.28,0:51:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.49,0:51:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cockpit was secured, locked from the inside.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}驾驶舱是封锁的 从里面锁上的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.70,0:51:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, were you inside, Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我猜猜 你进去过吧 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.16,0:51:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The co-pilot said the man just collapsed beside him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}副驾驶员说他就在旁边倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.62,0:51:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be induced anaphylaxis, I think it's called.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}应该是引发过敏 好像是这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.46,0:51:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Induced... What are you talking about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}引发… 你说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.51,0:51:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poisoning, I don't know how.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是下毒 我不知道怎么下的手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.43,0:51:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just he and the co-pilot, and the co-pilot, I trust.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有他和副驾驶员两人 副驾驶员我是信任的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.18,0:51:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}暂时还信任
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.26,0:51:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For now"? I don't know about this, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"暂时"？我对比没把握 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.56,0:51:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marenick, you need to transfer the money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}麦尼克 你需要转账这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.64,0:51:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Agent Hammond?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈蒙德特工在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.77,0:51:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to corroborate everything you're telling us.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要把你说的事跟他核实一下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.31,0:51:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hammond's dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈蒙德死了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.52,0:51:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.65,0:51:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He had cocaine in his carry-on. - Jesus Christ!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 他手提箱里有可卡因 - 老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.53,0:51:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confronted him, he pulled a gun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我质问他的时候 他拿出了枪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.90,0:52:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you serious? - Marenick. Transfer the money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你是认真的？- 麦尼克 转账这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.16,0:52:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me time. I'll find him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}争取点时间 我会查出他的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.45,0:52:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer the money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转账这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.66,0:52:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,$150 million into your account?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1.5亿美元转到你的账户？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.20,0:52:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something you're seriously asking me to do, Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 你真的要我这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.62,0:52:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment we land, arrest me, freeze the funds. Just transfer it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机一降落你就逮捕我 冻结账户 你转账就是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.71,0:52:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能这么做 比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.17,0:52:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The airline believes paying the demand\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}航空公司认为 支付赎金的话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.67,0:52:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will set a dangerous and irreversible precedent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}会造成无法挽回的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.59,0:52:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ, there are 150 people on this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是的 飞机上有150个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.80,0:52:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes me wonder why you haven't cut the network.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以我纳闷你怎么还没切断网络
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.80,0:52:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 150 people panicking,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}150个人在恐慌中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.18,0:52:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,contacting their families, while we're trying to handle the situation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我们尽力处理情况时 他们却在联系家人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.68,0:52:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You attribute all this to a passenger,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你把这事归因于乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.27,0:52:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can give me no proof he actually exists.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可你不能提供任何他存在的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.19,0:52:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cut the network. I need to communicate with this guy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能切断网络 我需要和他联系
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.19,0:52:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Agent Marks, I can't continue talking to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯特工 我不能继续和你谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.56,0:52:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.65,0:52:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means we will not negotiate with a terrorist.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}意思是我们不和恐怖分子谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.24,0:52:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.41,0:52:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else in the crew has access to the cockpit?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}乘务人员中还有谁有权进入驾驶舱？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.29,0:52:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.38,0:52:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see my phone, Agent Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要看看我的手机吗？马克斯特工
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.82,0:53:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your interview in the morning?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的面试是上午吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.32,0:53:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If we ever make it there.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 如果我们还能赶到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.95,0:53:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we ever land, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 除非能着陆的话 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.45,0:53:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. But it shouldn't...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错 不过应该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.95,0:53:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'll get up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起 我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.37,0:53:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Please, don't worry about it. Zack, this is Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用 没关系的 扎克 这是比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.75,0:53:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, Zack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.87,0:53:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking and Zack was telling me\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我刚才和他聊 扎克告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.17,0:53:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he's a programmer for smart phones.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是智能手机设计员
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.88,0:53:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.84,0:53:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm interviewing at Paige in the morning\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我上午要去佩奇公司面试
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.92,0:53:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a software analytics position.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}应聘一个软件分析的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.93,0:53:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which, technically, isn't programming. But...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}技术上说 不算编程 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.51,0:53:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm sorry for being such an asshole earlier...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 我很抱歉之前像个混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.31,0:53:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you were a programmer, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯 不过你是个程序员 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.60,0:53:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was telling him that I keep losing my phone,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我告诉他我经常找不到手机
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.52,0:53:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and because I keep my ringer off...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为我设置为静音…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.65,0:53:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if there was a way to find it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果有办法找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.15,0:54:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but apparently, it's pretty simple, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对 但其实很简单 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.86,0:54:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I didn't say it was simple... - GPS?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我没说简单… - GPS？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.99,0:54:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrier signal triangulation?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}载波信号三角定位？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.40,0:54:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.86,0:54:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you just send an intrusion virus attached to a picture text\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要发送一个彩信 附上侵入病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.03,0:54:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that switches the phone from silent to ring.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就能把手机从静音改为铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most phones load images automatically, so if you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}多数手机会自动装载 因此只要…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.16,0:54:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if there's no cell phone coverage?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如没有手机信号覆盖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.79,0:54:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's two phones on a smaller network?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如是小一点的网络的两部手机呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.34,0:54:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same protocol. Even over Wi-Fi.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}同样的做法 即使是无线网络
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.67,0:54:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How fast could you do something like that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你做这种事要多长时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.76,0:54:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, like right now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是说现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.84,0:54:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.93,0:54:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are variables.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这要看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.43,0:54:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone and the network.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}手机和网络
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.55,0:54:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the other phone is even turned on or not.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}另一部手机是否开机
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.56,0:54:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on. But the target number is anonymous.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开机 但手机号匿名
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.31,0:54:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to send it from this phone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只能从这个手机发送
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.61,0:54:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.74,0:54:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshal, I don't know about this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道这是否合适
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.15,0:54:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.32,0:54:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dude is talking about killing people. Can he see us right now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这个人威胁要杀人 他现在能看到我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.12,0:54:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.08,0:54:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can give it a shot. But I can't guarantee...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以试一下 但我保证不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.58,0:54:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How fast?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要多长时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.91,0:54:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty minutes?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}30分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:54:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}20分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.29,0:55:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have less than eight minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们只有不到8分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.67,0:55:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it. That's why they want to hire you, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能行的 所以他们才想聘用你 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.22,0:55:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}8分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.47,0:55:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.09,0:55:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me when it's ready.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了跟我说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.01,0:55:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, ma'am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.82,0:55:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see up there?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在驾驶舱看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.49,0:55:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not at liberty to say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能说的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.78,0:55:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you like a doctor or something?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是医生什么的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.58,0:55:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.20,0:55:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, if I can have your attention.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.46,0:55:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The business cabin is now closed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}商务舱现在关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.50,0:55:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, the business cabin is now closed to everyone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}商务舱现在禁止任何人进入
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.84,0:55:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight attendants, if you could do your best,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空乘人员 请你们尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.93,0:55:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please, to accommodate all passengers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}安排所有乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.01,0:55:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.35,0:56:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a family, for Christ's sake!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我还有家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.06,0:56:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a situation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们遇到情况
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.06,0:56:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, you gonna tell us what the hell is going on or not?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你到底告不告诉我们出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.32,0:56:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the captain all right or not?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长情况怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.49,0:56:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The... The situation is quite complicated.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这… 这情况很复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.07,0:56:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complicated? Come on!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}复杂？拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.32,0:56:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can assure you...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我向你们保证…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.66,0:56:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bullshit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.91,0:56:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's in hand!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都在控制中
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.08,0:56:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is under control!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都在控制中
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.45,0:56:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, calm down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大家都镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.42,0:56:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the captain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要见见机长
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.88,0:56:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head up there myself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.55,0:56:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Move aside, Marshal.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}受不了了 让开 空警
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.80,0:56:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait. Free travel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等等 免费旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.67,0:56:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free flights!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}免费飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.47,0:56:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free travel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}免费旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.84,0:56:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The airline company will guarantee\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}航空公司会保证
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.30,0:56:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one year's international free travel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为期一年的免费国际旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.68,0:56:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sit down, remain quiet, and do what I say.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要你们坐下 保持安静 照我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.89,0:56:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free international travel.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}免费国际旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.90,0:56:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.32,0:56:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twelve months.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}12个月
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.77,0:56:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}免费
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.03,0:56:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guaranteed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保证
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.28,0:56:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One year. Free travel. Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一年 免费旅行 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.74,0:56:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle, it's Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔 我是比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.91,0:56:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we turning?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么掉头？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.99,0:57:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been instructed not to communicate with you, Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我被指示不和你交流 马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.20,0:57:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they tell you to cut the network? Listen to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们告诉你切断网络了吗？听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.38,0:57:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The men who issued those instructions are not on this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}指示你的人不在这飞机上
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.55,0:57:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your plane. These are your passengers. Rice!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是你的飞机 他们是你的乘客 赖斯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.84,0:57:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.88,0:57:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been diverted north. 55 minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们转向北方已经55分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.60,0:57:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they tell you to cut the network?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们告诉你切断网络了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.01,0:57:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have orders, Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有命令在身 马克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.93,0:57:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me five minutes. Five minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给我五分钟 五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.35,0:57:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Land the plane wherever you want,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想在哪里降落都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.85,0:57:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but do not switch that network off.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但不要切断网络
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.31,0:57:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me? I have a plan. I can find this guy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听见了吗？我有个计划 我能查出这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.98,0:57:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.58,0:57:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can trust this guy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但愿他能信得过
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.91,0:57:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.16,0:57:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I'd rather not end up an accessory to a hijacking.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可不想担上劫机同案犯的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.71,0:57:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay. - Zack.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 好了 - 扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.42,0:57:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done. Here it is.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.71,0:57:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.63,0:57:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the captain's still in control of the plane?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你觉得机长还在控制着飞机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.80,0:57:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane almost goes down,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机差点坠毁
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.39,0:58:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a guy waving his gun around, tying people up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这个人挥舞着枪 还绑人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.93,0:58:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say he pretty much took control.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看是他控制着飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.81,0:58:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think the thing about free international flights was bullshit, or...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么国际免费旅行只是他信口开河？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.02,0:58:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At what point do we do something?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们什么时候才做点什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.90,0:58:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, would you please return to your seats?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}诸位 请回到自己座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.90,0:58:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what's going on either, do you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你也不知道什么情况 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.76,0:58:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the air marshal up to now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个空警现在要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.89,0:58:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.14,0:58:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need every passenger to raise their hands above their heads\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有人把手举到头上
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.48,0:58:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and remain silent for the next 60 seconds.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保持沉默60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.15,0:58:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a request.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这不是请求
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.53,0:58:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.45,0:59:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight attendants, too.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也包括乘务人员
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.20,0:59:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}举起来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.22,1:00:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hands behind your head. - What the fuck...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 手放在脑后 - 你他妈…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.10,1:00:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands behind your goddamn head!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}手放在脑后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.48,1:00:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove the phone. With one hand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一只手把手机拿出来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.03,1:00:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that phone before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我从未见过这部手机
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.20,1:00:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, undo his seatbelt.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小姐 解开他的安全带
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.20,1:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.83,1:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You searched me. My phone was in my bag.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你搜查过我 我的手机在我包里
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.75,1:00:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the aisle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到过道上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.04,1:00:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you think I've done...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不管你以为我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.54,1:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Front of the plane. Move!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}闭嘴 到飞机前面 走
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.38,1:00:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a mistake.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这是犯了错误
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.96,1:00:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转过身
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.97,1:00:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}轻点
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.34,1:00:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.93,1:00:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, please! That's not my phone!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听我说 拜托 这不是我的手机
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.23,1:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a passenger!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是个乘客
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.81,1:00:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you open the account in my name?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么在我的名下开账户？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.52,1:00:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.81,1:00:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question, or I will break your arm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回答问题 否则扭断你的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.44,1:01:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got the wrong guy!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你抓错人了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.62,1:01:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found him, Nancy. We got him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们找到他了 南希 查到他了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.83,1:01:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me? Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么是我？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.66,1:01:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么是我？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.00,1:01:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.50,1:01:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, get the doctor. Now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 叫医生来 快
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.49,1:02:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill? Bill?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔？比尔？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.26,1:02:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's break this down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 我们分析一下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.86,1:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, he ties up that guy, then he takes another guy and brings him out back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他先是绑了这个人 然后又抓走了另一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.81,1:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is he gonna pick us off one by one?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是要一个个的除掉我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the doctor right there. Hey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}医生来了 喂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.48,1:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to let us all know what's going on?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要告诉我们怎么回事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.87,1:02:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And the captain? - Dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 机长呢？- 死了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.91,1:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The co-pilot is flying. Behind locked doors.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}副驾驶员在锁着的驾驶舱内驾驶
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.76,1:02:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you all right? - Me? Fine. I'm great.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你怎么样？- 我？我没事 我挺好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.76,1:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be seeing all this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不该让你看到这一幕的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.85,1:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Doc. So, we got a dead passenger and a dead pilot.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这么说 死了一个乘客和机长
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.85,1:03:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane took a hard turn 15 minutes ago.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}15分钟前飞机急转弯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.77,1:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't happen mid-flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这不该在飞行途中发生的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.61,1:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The marshal closed off business class,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空警封锁了商务舱
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.03,1:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,moved all the passengers to the back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把乘客都赶到后面
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.41,1:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this scenario ring any bells?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这一场景是否似曾相识？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.49,1:03:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he's gonna crash the plane?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你觉得他打算让飞机坠毁？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.06,1:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight 10, this is Royal Air Force 114,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}10次航班 我是英国空军114号
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.35,1:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call sign Jackrabbit. How copy?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呼号长耳大野兔 能收到吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.40,1:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.70,1:05:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told I could stay here with my husband.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她们说我可以和丈夫坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.41,1:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.82,1:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used the lavatory about an hour ago. Do you remember that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你1个小时前去过卫生间 还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.20,1:05:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have Alzheimer's.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我并没有老年痴呆症
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.70,1:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know if someone else went in there after you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道随后还有谁进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.75,1:05:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she was standing there blocking the aisle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 她站在那儿挡住了过道
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.46,1:05:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.59,1:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The redhead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个红发女
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.21,1:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman you were sitting next to.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐在你身边的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.23,1:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in here?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你到这里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.98,1:05:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drinking. I'm sorry, I shouldn't. That's just terrible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在喝酒 对不起 这样很不好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.82,1:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在想
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.86,1:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the window seat?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何非要靠窗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.53,1:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why the window seat?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？为何非要靠窗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.58,1:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you sit next to me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何要坐在我旁边？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.91,1:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What? - I found a hole\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么？- 我在商务舱卫生间
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.70,1:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the first class toilet, clear shot to the captain.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}发现一个洞 能直接射中机长
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.96,1:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who died had one of these imbedded in his skin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个死了的人皮肤上有这个
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.46,1:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever seen one before?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.09,1:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.26,1:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toilets were locked 10 minutes before the captain died.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机长死前10分钟 卫生间是锁着的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.51,1:06:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes before that, I saw a woman enter.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}此前5分钟 我看到一个女人进去
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.47,1:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's 70 years old.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她70岁了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.22,1:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you went in after her,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她说你是随后进去的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.18,1:06:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she doesn't have Alzheimer's, if you're wondering.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}另外她也没有老年痴呆症
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.98,1:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me if I saw someone else go in,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是问我是否看见别人进去
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.15,1:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or if I killed the captain?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还是问我是否杀了机长呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.99,1:06:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see someone else?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你看到别人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.86,1:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.12,1:06:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then answer the question.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就回答问题
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.20,1:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.04,1:06:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You switched seats to be next to me, which made you trustworthy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你换座位到我身边 博得我的信赖
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.62,1:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You engaged me in conversation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你和我攀谈
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.25,1:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To relax you because you were scared...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了让你放松 因为你很害怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.34,1:06:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you evaded personal questions.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可你避开私人问题
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.54,1:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, like where I work. Yeah, that's a great personal question.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的工作地点当然是私人问题
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.46,1:06:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You inserted yourself into the investigation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你主动参与调查
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.97,1:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是认真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.22,1:06:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tracking the phone, that was your idea.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}追踪手机就是你的点子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.68,1:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.89,1:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only person on this plane who has stood by you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是飞机上唯一站在你这边的人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been lying to me this entire time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而你一直对我撒谎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.81,1:07:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been lying to me since the second you boarded this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你从登机起就对我撒谎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.89,1:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God! Okay, fine, fine!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.94,1:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago my heart failed,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}七年前我心脏衰竭
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.61,1:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was dead for like 43 minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}死亡了43分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.28,1:07:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aortic arch aneurysm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}主动脉弓瘤
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.11,1:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They tried to fix it, but when I woke up,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}医生试图治疗 但当我醒来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.28,1:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they told me it was something they couldn't fix\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们说治不了这个病
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.95,1:07:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that one day it would fail again and I would just die.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将来还会复发 然后我就死了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.45,1:07:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's okay with me because we're all gonna die someday,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我无所谓 因为人人将来都会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.92,1:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and none of us know when it's gonna be, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且谁也不知道会在哪一天 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.46,1:07:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I fly, which is a lot,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但当我乘飞机时 经常乘飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.30,1:07:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to look out the window instead of\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜欢看着窗外
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.05,1:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the back of the seat in front of me\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而不是前面的座椅
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.72,1:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a folding tray table, because one day might be today.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是折叠餐桌 因为保不准就死在今天
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.47,1:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you like the aisle?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你又为何喜欢靠过道座位呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.06,1:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.11,1:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.32,1:08:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.66,1:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pour you a real drink.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给你倒一杯真正的酒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.50,1:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.46,1:08:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.01,1:08:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate flying.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我讨厌飞行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.60,1:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.52,1:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always kind of liked it, you know?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直挺喜欢的 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.18,1:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six hours in the same spot, nobody can get to you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}6个小时呆在同一地点 没人能来找你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.77,1:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do but just be present, you know?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无事可做 只是呆在那里 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.36,1:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no control.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真是毫无控制
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.52,1:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control is an illusion. There is no control.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}控制只是假象 不存在控制
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.03,1:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over anything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对任何事
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.66,1:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to listen to this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你来听听这个
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.37,1:08:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where a federal bomb squad and investigators are searching\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}联邦拆弹小组和调查员正在搜查
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.62,1:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a car that allegedly belongs to Bill Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一辆据称是比尔·马克斯的汽车
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.33,1:08:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sources tel! us that Marks parked his car here at the airport today\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}消息称 在登上英国亚奎兰蒂航空公司10次航班之前
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.46,1:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before boarding British Aqualantic Flight 10,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯把他的车停在机场
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.30,1:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way he had boarded so many flights before,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他以前多次登机
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.89,1:09:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the guise of an everyday passenger,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}表面是普通乘客
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.22,1:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but carrying a mandate\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其实肩负着
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.64,1:09:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the United States Department of Homeland Security.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国国土安全部分派的任务
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.48,1:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His job, to protect the flight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他的职责是保护航班
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.73,1:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was also, as always, carrying a concealed handgun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他也携带一把隐藏的手枪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.56,1:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we know this is the hijacker's phone. Can it tell us anything?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们知道这是劫机者的手机 能据此查出什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.32,1:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's password protected. I can't get in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有密码保护 我进不去
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.74,1:09:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try guessing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有没有猜下密码？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.75,1:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a transatlantic flight from New York to London,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是一架从纽约飞往伦敦的跨大西洋航班
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.88,1:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the airline now confirming this is,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}航空公司已经确认
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.30,1:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in fact, a hijacking in progress.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}正在发生劫机
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.05,1:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What did you do? - I didn't do anything, I swear to God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你做了什么？- 我什么都没做 我对天发誓
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.39,1:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just was messing around with it. I didn't do anything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是随便摆弄了一下 什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.28,1:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open every bag in this cabin.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}打开客舱中所有的包
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.45,1:10:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the horrific twist is that the hijacker\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可怕的是 这个劫机者
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.95,1:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now believed to be the one person who\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拒信正是这个
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.79,1:10:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was authorized to carry a gun onto the plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有权携带枪支上飞机的人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.62,1:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for a package. You'll know if you find it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要寻找一个包裹 看到后肯定能认出来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.88,1:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Every bag. Go! Now! - Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 每个包 快去 - 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.38,1:10:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marenick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}麦尼克
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.46,1:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Marks? - Order this plane down to 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 马克斯？- 命令这架飞机下降到8千英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.01,1:10:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks, listen to me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯 听我说
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.34,1:10:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have reason to believe there's a bomb on the plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有理由相信飞机上有个炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.97,1:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agent Marks, just listen to me. - We need to drop altitude now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 马克斯 听我说 - 我们需要降低高度
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.10,1:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb at this height would tear this plane apart.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这么高的话 炸弹会让飞机散架
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.14,1:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and questions already swirling around\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有疑问都集中到比尔·马克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.22,1:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill Marks and his state of mind\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和他登机时
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.23,1:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as he boarded the flight...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}的精神状态…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.69,1:10:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, when you send me a text and you say\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 你给我发短信说
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.15,1:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're out of options, you and I both know that's not the case.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你已没别的选择了 你也知道不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.36,1:10:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else received that message?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有谁收到这一短信的？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.19,1:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, we got it here at TSA.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}显然我们运输安全局是收到了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.94,1:10:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting calls from the FBI, the White House,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们还接到FBI 白宫的电话
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.90,1:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now the press is involved.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如今媒体也卷入进来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.49,1:10:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have our attention. There's no need to take this any further, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你已经成功得到了关注 没必要再做别的啥事了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.95,1:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else has to die. I know it feels like no one is listening, but I am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用再有人死 我知道你感觉没人在聆听你 但我在听
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.58,1:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work it out together.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们好商量
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.75,1:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marenick, you're not getting this!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}麦尼克 你不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.29,1:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, listen to me. Let's talk this through.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 听我说 我们把事情谈开
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.92,1:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking to me like I'm a terrorist.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听你的口气 仿佛我是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.71,1:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how this works.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道规矩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.84,1:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to bring that plane any lower into civilian airspace,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你要把飞机下降到民用空域
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.51,1:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be shot down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会被击落的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.01,1:11:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a threat to ground, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会对地面造成威胁
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.68,1:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for your money and sit tight.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你安稳等着你的钱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.22,1:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stark picture of a man in a dangerous psychological state.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}显然是一个处于危险精神状态的人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.27,1:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, stay with me. I need you to cooperate with us...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 和我保持通话 你要与我们合作…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.19,1:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.23,1:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officials say he was originally from Northern Ireland.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}官方称他出身于北爱尔兰
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.77,1:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became a decorated New York City\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}成为一个优秀纽约警察
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.73,1:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,police officer with a young family.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一个年轻的家庭
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.69,1:11:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became distraught when his 8-year-old daughter, Olivia,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在他八岁的女儿奥利维亚因癌症病逝时
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.57,1:11:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,passed away from cancer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他悲痛欲绝
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.28,1:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the next decade, sources say he became withdrawn,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}之后10年 消息称他变得孤僻
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.16,1:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got divorced in 2003.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}2003年离婚
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.33,1:11:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspended and later fired from the NYPD,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}被停职 之后被纽约警察局解雇
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.46,1:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was then, in the summer of 2003,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后在2003年夏
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.08,1:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he transferred to the Federal Air Marshal Service.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他被调到联邦空警部门
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.59,1:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there, his colleagues and neighbors\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在那里 他的同事和邻居
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.59,1:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying he's a quiet man who kept mostly to himself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}说他很内向 不常与人交往
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.30,1:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a costly program, as well.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这一部门耗费也很高
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.59,1:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question. This is what happens when you put an unstable,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}毫无疑问 让一个精神不稳 充满愤怒的人拥有权力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.39,1:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,angry man in a position of power.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.10,1:11:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy wasn't even born in the U. S.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}此人甚至不是在美国出生的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.73,1:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could be IRA, for all we know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是爱尔兰共和军的都有可能
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.31,1:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.39,1:12:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since 9/11, we've put 4,000 air marshals in the sky.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在911之后 我们在飞机上派了4千名空警
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.61,1:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do these people come from?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些人都来自哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.15,1:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen these guys myself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我亲眼见过这种人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.78,1:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They walk right past the security line\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们径直走过警戒线
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.90,1:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're barely qualified to carry a badge.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}根本不配携带警徽
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.99,1:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walked right past security.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}径直走过警戒线
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.99,1:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's controversy around the air marshal program already.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}围绕着空警部门 已经有过不少非议
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.20,1:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the final blow?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这次是致命一击吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.94,1:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We give these people absolute power in the sky.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们让这些人在飞机上拥有特权
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.76,1:12:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We give them guns and we put them on planes,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给他们发枪 让他们到飞机上
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.58,1:12:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're surprised when we have incidences of drug smuggling.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当出现走私毒品时 我们却惊讶
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.33,1:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.64,1:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}动手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.18,1:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, go!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快 快
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.40,1:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab him! Grab him! Get the gun!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抓住他 抓住他 夺枪
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.94,1:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Help me, man! - Wait!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 帮帮我 - 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.07,1:13:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.53,1:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop it! - No, no, no, no.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 住手 - 不 不
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.82,1:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.91,1:13:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take him down! Kick his ass! - Somebody stop him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 打倒他 揍他 - 来人阻止他
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.92,1:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.25,1:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.92,1:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.55,1:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, man!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.72,1:13:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of him!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放开他
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.43,1:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住手
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.07,1:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him to the ground! Hold him steady!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把他按在地上 按住他
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.36,1:14:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get his legs!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱住他的腿
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.40,1:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him, God damn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}按住他
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.82,1:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Grab his legs! - Listen to me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 抱住他的腿 - 听我说
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.61,1:14:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Listen to me! - Shut up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 听我说 - 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.70,1:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, please! Please, go into the bathroom!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听我说 去卫生间看看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.16,1:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pin him down! - In the bathroom!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 把他按倒 - 去卫生间看看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.45,1:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're done, Marshal! - There's a dead body!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你完了 空警 - 里面有具尸体
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.24,1:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! Shut up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.37,1:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a dead body and a briefcase!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}里面有具尸体和一个手提箱
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.50,1:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the briefcase you'll find a bomb!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}手提箱里有个炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.83,1:14:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit, you're lying!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}胡说 你在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.25,1:14:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a bomb on this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这架飞机上有个炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.34,1:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me, please!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}相信我 拜托
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.13,1:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放开他
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.34,1:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said get off of him! Get off him!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我让你们放开他 放开他
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.68,1:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now. Get back, back!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快点 退后 退后
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.64,1:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back away, all of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们都退后
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.35,1:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what you're doing with that gun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不要拿着枪胡来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.14,1:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. What is he doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 他在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.81,1:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowen, give me the gun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}博文 把钱给我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.06,1:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Tom, please. - No, stay where you are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 汤姆 拜托 - 你站在这里别动
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.90,1:14:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm NYPD, we got it covered! Put it down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是纽约警察 我们控制了局势 把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.32,1:14:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a bomb on this plane?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机上有炸弹吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.25,1:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me what the hell is going on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要你告诉我是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.25,1:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Relax. - Don't tell me to relax!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 放松 - 别让我放松
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.88,1:15:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A passenger on board this flight has\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这航班上有一个乘客
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.50,1:15:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,threatened to kill someone every 20 minutes\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他威胁每20分钟杀一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.38,1:15:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless they're paid $150 million.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非他们拿到1.5亿美元
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.80,1:15:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, three people are dead.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在已经死了3个人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.35,1:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb will explode in less than half an hour.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那炸弹还有不到半小时就爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.94,1:15:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, they want you to believe that I'm responsible.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们希望你们认为我是嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.40,1:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you've heard about me is true.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}新闻上对我的介绍都是事实
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.61,1:15:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost my family, my job. I'm an alcoholic.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我失去了家人 工作 我是个酒鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.57,1:15:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter was diagnosed with acute leukemia at the age of five,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我女儿5岁时诊断有急性白血病
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.70,1:15:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I spent my days at work instead of being at home,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而我整天在警局里 却不在家里陪她
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.12,1:15:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking after her, because I was afraid of watching her die!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}照顾她 因为我害怕看着她死
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.80,1:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a good father. I'm not a good man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不是个好人 不是好父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.14,1:16:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hijacking this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不是打算劫持这架飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.14,1:16:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to save it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是为了拯救它
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.60,1:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will save it! If you work with me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而我肯定能拯救 只要你们与我合作
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.24,1:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're NYPD. So was I,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是纽约警察 我也曾经是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.82,1:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you look as if you were a better officer than I was.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感觉你比我当年要强
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.33,1:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut him loose. Nancy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给他松绑 南希
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.88,1:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to start moving all the luggage towards the back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们需要开始把行李运到后部
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.63,1:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And move the women and children,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让妇女和儿童
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.89,1:16:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move them up to the front of the plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转移到飞机前部
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.89,1:16:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your plan?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这就是你的计划？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.22,1:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to prepare for the worst possible outcome.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的职责是应对最糟糕的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.77,1:16:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my job is to prevent it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的职责是防止这种情况
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.60,1:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women and children, no exceptions. Men move up in coach.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妇女和儿童 没有例外 男人去经济舱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.65,1:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你他妈到底在想什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.90,1:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a plan of action that exists\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}存在一个行动预案
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.19,1:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called the Least Resistant Bomb Location Protocol.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}叫做"最小阻力爆炸位置预案"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.61,1:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You place the bomb against the rear door\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把炸弹放在后门
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.70,1:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stack anything and everything against it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上面堆放很多东西
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.83,1:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every bag, blanket, every pillow. Nullify it as best you can.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}全部的包 毛毯 枕头 尽力抵消爆炸力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.12,1:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this height a bomb would tear this plane apart,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在这个高度 炸弹会让飞机散架
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.92,1:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we descend to 8,000 feet, pressure equalizes,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我们下降到8千英尺的话 压力平衡
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.38,1:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then we have a chance.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么我们还有机会
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.72,1:17:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just gonna let the bomb go off?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么你就任由炸弹爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.89,1:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, I'm gonna stop it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然不是 我要阻止它
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.64,1:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't, I'd rather be prepared, wouldn't you?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但如果阻止不了 还是有所准备的好 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.98,1:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who brought this bomb on the plane may try something.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把炸弹带上飞机的人不会束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.94,1:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I trust you to stop him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能指望你制伏他吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.65,1:17:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're damn straight you can.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你放心就是
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.20,1:17:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reilly, sorry about the nose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雷利 对不起打断了你的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.37,1:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was never my best feature.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}反正以前的模样也不好看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.83,1:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get them to wire the money? Just try something?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能不能让他们转账？试试办法
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.88,1:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was never about the money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们不是为了钱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.29,1:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's it about?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.38,1:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. They used an account in my name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我拿不准 他们用我名下的一个账户
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.59,1:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want an air marshal to take down a plane\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们希望一个法警劫持一架飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.51,1:18:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with 150 people on board,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}劫持150人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.10,1:18:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they want the whole world to see it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们还想让世人看到这一幕
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.47,1:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never supposed to find that bomb.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我本不该找到炸弹的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.36,1:18:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.45,1:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这可不是好事
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.32,1:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道这意味着什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.29,1:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqualantic Flight 10, this is Royal Air Force 114,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚奎兰蒂航空10次航班 我是英国空军114号
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.00,1:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call sign Jackrabbit. How copy?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呼号长耳大野兔 能收到吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.67,1:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy, Jackrabbit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}收到 长耳大野兔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.55,1:18:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be your escorts to the designated landing zone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们将护送你去指定降落区
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.26,1:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not deviate from your current course\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不得私自改变
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.13,1:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or altitude without authorization.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}目前航线及高度
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.97,1:18:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you copy? - Copy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 能收到吗？- 收到
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.68,1:18:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.10,1:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kyle. - Yes, Marks?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 凯尔 - 什么？马克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.48,1:18:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new situation.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出现了新情况
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.52,1:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no shit.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那还用说
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.44,1:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to drop the plane to 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要你把飞机降到8千英尺高度
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.81,1:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the lowest pressure deferential you can.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尽量去气压差最小的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.19,1:19:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One PSI, 1.5 at most.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1个大气压 最多1.5个
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.36,1:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Bill, that's explosives protocol.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等等 比尔 这可是爆炸预案
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.40,1:19:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have 16 minutes, give or take.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我们还有16分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.78,1:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know we have company, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道来了别的飞机 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.20,1:19:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two typhoons are flanking me right now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}两架台风喷气机正在我的侧翼
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.21,1:19:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're watching, and you want me to...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你让我在他们眼皮底下…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.17,1:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle, we need to drop altitude now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔 我们要马上下降高度
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.83,1:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I have orders, Marks. Any suspicious activity and they...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 我接到命令 马克斯 有任何可疑举动的话…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.26,1:19:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赖斯
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.67,1:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a bomb on this plane. We have to descend to 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机上有个炸弹 我们必须降到8千英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.18,1:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AH right, give me 10 minutes. If we drop now, I lose speed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 给我10分钟 如果现在下降 我会减速
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.89,1:19:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes at this altitude, maybe I can get us close enough,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在这个高度10分钟 也许我们就能接近冰岛
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.72,1:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,close enough to land in Iceland.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以开始降落到冰岛上
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.48,1:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes. Thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}10分钟 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.67,1:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an RDX explosive. Very professional. Maybe military.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是RDX炸弹 很专业 可能是军方的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.05,1:20:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that blow?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这东西能爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.97,1:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you positive it can't be disarmed?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你确定能拆除吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.35,1:20:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a calibrated pressure trigger.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是标准压力触发器
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.31,1:20:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to disarm a bomb is to remove the trigger.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拆除炸弹的唯一方式就是拆掉触发器
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.06,1:20:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But remove the trigger, the pressure releases, the bomb goes off.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但拆掉触发器的话 压力释放 炸弹就会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.74,1:20:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, can't we just dump it? - Same principle in reverse.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 把它扔出去不行吗？- 也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.90,1:20:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The low pressure outside the plane\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机外的低气压
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.82,1:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't hold the trigger. You try to dump it...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}维持不了触发器 扔出去的话…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.62,1:20:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb goes off.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}炸弹就会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.70,1:20:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Isn't there like a wire you can cut? - No.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 没有什么电线可以切断吗？- 没有
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.91,1:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if this guy doesn't get his money,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么如果这个人拿不到钱
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.50,1:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's gonna kill himself and everyone aboard?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他就把自己和飞机上所有一起炸死？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.04,1:20:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this. This is crazy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真不敢相信这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.67,1:20:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why aren't we looking for this guy? - We're out of time.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们为啥不去找这个人呢？- 我们没时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.63,1:20:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bullshit answer, Marshal, you know it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是荒唐的回答 空警
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.34,1:20:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别冲动
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.55,1:20:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 150 passengers and crew. It could be anyone.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}乘客和乘务人员有150个人 说不定是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.17,1:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find him! Let's pay him, let's do something.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们去找他 给他钱 做点什么
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.93,1:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about the money, and even if I find him...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他不是为了钱 即使我找到了他…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.76,1:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he ever intended to get off this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想他也没打算活着下飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.22,1:21:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God, we're all gonna die.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 我们都要死了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.23,1:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不会
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.15,1:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta place the bomb here. Stack all available luggage over it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要把炸弹放在这里 把所有可用行李堆在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.44,1:21:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And direct the explosion outward.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把爆炸力引向外面
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.11,1:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 8,000 feet, the pressure will equalize. Then we land.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在8千英尺高度 内外气压会平衡 然后我们着陆
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.53,1:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- With a hole in the fuselage? - And this has worked before?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 机身有个大洞情况下降落？- 这招奏效过吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.95,1:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never been tried before.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}从未试过这一招
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.00,1:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That you know of. - You're not being helpful, Doctor.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 试过你也不知道 - 说这些没用 医生
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.92,1:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so screwed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们死定了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.12,1:21:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could work! We've got to try!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有可能成功的 我们必须试试
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.29,1:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Grab every able hand! Let's get this done!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快 让能帮忙的人都来 我们办妥这件事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.09,1:21:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshal, if they're setting this thing off, no matter what,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空警 既然他们肯定要引爆炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.34,1:21:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what are they waiting for?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何还要等一段时间？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.30,1:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just grab what you can, go to the back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿上你能拿的东西 去机后
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.39,1:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you guys form a chain,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们几个接力
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.81,1:21:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,send those bags back as fast as you can.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尽快把行李传递过去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.94,1:21:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remove all luggage from the overhead bins.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请取出头顶行李舱的所有行李
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.95,1:22:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyle, how close are we? We need to descend, now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凯尔 我们还有多远？我们现在得马上下降
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.16,1:22:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, give me three minutes.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 给我3分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.37,1:22:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes, okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}3分钟 好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.29,1:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your watch. Three minutes from now, not a second longer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看你的表 3分钟后 1秒也不能耽搁
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.88,1:22:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, drop down 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无论如何都要下降到8千英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.17,1:22:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.26,1:22:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take this. - Lighter luggage up front.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 拿着 - 先放轻行李
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.80,1:22:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep piling please. Bring the heavier luggage down.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}继续堆放 重行李的放下面
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.80,1:22:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep them going.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}持续传递
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.85,1:22:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, keep that with you, I just need...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 这个留着 我只需要…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.39,1:22:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.69,1:22:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's bleeding, thanks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对 在出血 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.65,1:22:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a displaced fracture.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有移位性骨折
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.31,1:22:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's a broken nose, it's normal, I don't need you to fix it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是鼻子破了而已 很正常 不需要你治疗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.28,1:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm going to set your nose.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要让你的鼻子复位
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.32,1:22:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hold this.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给 拿着
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.82,1:22:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make it quick, all right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就快一点 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.95,1:22:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apply some pressure.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}施点压力
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.78,1:22:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.74,1:22:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On three. One...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}数3下 1…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.38,1:22:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart, you've got to come out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}孩子 你必须出来
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.92,1:22:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'll hold your hand. But it's not safe.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没事的 我会拉着你的手 这里不安全
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.38,1:22:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Gwen, what's going on? - Please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 格温 怎么了？- 拜托
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.97,1:22:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们得快点
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.34,1:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm sorry, I need your help. She won't come out.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起 我需要你帮忙 她不肯出来
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.06,1:23:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you scared?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了？你害怕？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.39,1:23:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see my daddy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想见爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.44,1:23:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you do, sweetheart. I know you do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道 孩子 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.61,1:23:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I was a daddy once to a little girl just like you,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也曾是你这样的小姑娘的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.32,1:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when she was scared, you know what she'd do?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当她害怕时 你知道她做什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.41,1:23:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a magic ribbon, very powerful.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她有个魔法丝带 法力强大
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.12,1:23:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll protect you, just like your daddy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它能保护你 就像你爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.04,1:23:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna see it? I have it in my pocket.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想看看吗？就在我的口袋里
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.08,1:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carry it all the time. Here it is. Here.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直随身带着 给
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.38,1:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrap it around your hand, just like that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}绕在手上 像这样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.51,1:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, hold on to it now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对 现在把它攥紧了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.51,1:23:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bribing me?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是想收买我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.43,1:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.73,1:23:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend, Jen. She's gonna look after you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是我朋友珍妮 她会照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.40,1:23:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jen, this is Becca. - Hey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 珍妮 这是贝嘉 - 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.86,1:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll see your father soon. I promise.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放心 你会很快见到爸爸 我保证
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.28,1:23:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have the window seat?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能坐在靠窗的座位吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.45,1:24:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this old seat? Mm-hm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是说这个老旧的座位？嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.17,1:24:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, we 're about to begin our descent.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位乘客 我们就要开始下降了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.63,1:24:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to return to your seats and fasten your seatbelts.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你们回到座位上 系紧安全带
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.21,1:24:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay calm. Everyone, please get back to your seats.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请各位保持镇静 回到自己座位上
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.88,1:24:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.97,1:24:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marks, we transferred the money,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马克斯 我们已经转账
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.60,1:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150 million US into your account.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1.5亿美元已经到了你的账户
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.18,1:24:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for the money. Whatever he's doing...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在转账来不及了 不管他目的何在…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.31,1:24:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop now, Marks. You have your money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可以收手了 马克斯 你已经拿到了钱
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.77,1:24:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jets will escort you in.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喷气机会护送你降落
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.94,1:24:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to bring this plane down to 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我必须让飞机下降到8千英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.81,1:24:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not descend into civilian airspace.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不能下降到民用空域
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.15,1:24:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he wants the money? You think that will stop him?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以为他要的是钱？你以为这就能让他收手？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.78,1:24:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you transferred the money, prove it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你已经转账 证明一下
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.03,1:24:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want proof? Here's your proof, $150 million was transferred\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要证明？给你证明 1.5亿美元
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.78,1:24:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to account CH-1000-23000-A-10982.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已转至账户CH 1000 23000 A 10982
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.16,1:24:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmation code R48940.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}确认码 R48940
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.50,1:24:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll escort you into a military air field,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们会护送你进入军用空域
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.05,1:25:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will not be arrested, no questions will be asked.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不会逮捕你 也不会问你什么
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.68,1:25:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a bomb on this plane. It isn't mine. It will go off!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}机上有个炸弹 不是我的 肯定会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.97,1:25:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And we have to prepare... - You're in command of a hijacked vessel\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们要应对… - 你控制着一架被劫持客机
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.85,1:25:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will not dive that plane into civilian airspace.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不得把飞机下降到民用空域
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.52,1:25:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.60,1:25:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Marks, God damn it, we will shoot you down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么我们就击落你
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.35,1:25:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, they'll fish this plane's black box out of the Atlantic Ocean,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等将来 会有人从大西洋底打捞出飞机的黑匣子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.86,1:25:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world will know these people could have been saved.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世人就会知道这些人本可免于一死
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.86,1:25:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world already knows what's going on\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世人已经知道飞机上的事
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.44,1:25:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in that plane, Bill. You are hijacking it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}被你劫持了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.90,1:25:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's what you're telling them. - No, no, no, no, no.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 那是你这么说的 - 不 不 不
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.45,1:25:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what your hostages are telling them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是你的人质说的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.20,1:25:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That video is playing on every major news network on repeat, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那段视频正在各大新闻网反复播放
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.41,1:25:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What video? - One of your hostages uploaded a video.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 什么视频？- 你的一名人质上传的视频
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.33,1:25:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking a man, dragging him around at gunpoint,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你抓了个人 拿枪顶着他
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.83,1:25:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stumbling over terrified passengers.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在害怕的乘客中走过去
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.83,1:25:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect us to believe anything that you're saying\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们还怎么相信你的话
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.38,1:25:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you clearly are abusing those hostages?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你显然在虐待人质嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.46,1:25:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seen everything we need to know.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都已经看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.21,1:25:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're trying to negotiate...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可我们依然和你协商…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.26,1:25:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone, now! The phone!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的手机 交出来
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.39,1:25:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the video that you uploaded! Come on!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我看看你上传的视频 快
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.23,1:26:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my son.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我代儿子道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.95,1:26:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humor me. Look!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帮我看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.95,1:26:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Look. - I don't see him.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 看 - 我没看到他
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.62,1:26:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, look.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看看
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.08,1:26:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right there. - Where?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 在那里 - 哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.71,1:26:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses. Come on, move.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个戴眼镜的 快点 过去
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.88,1:26:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.92,1:26:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You. Look...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你 看着我…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.43,1:26:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.95,1:26:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay where you are.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别过来
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.49,1:26:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, don't test me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 别把我逼急了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.66,1:26:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.29,1:26:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reilly, drop!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雷利 低头
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.54,1:27:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reilly, get down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雷利 趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.25,1:27:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me an unloaded weapon?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你给我没子弹的枪？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.51,1:27:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overhead bin, 4B!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}舱顶行李箱 4B
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.76,1:27:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, down! Stay down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大家都趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.06,1:27:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, get out of there, move! - What?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嘿 离开那 让开 - 什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.89,1:27:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嘿 伙计
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.15,1:27:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looking for this?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在找它吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.78,1:27:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}给我
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.49,1:27:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.71,1:27:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get back! - Okay, okay.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 后退 - 好 好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.17,1:27:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jackrabbit, I have shots fired outside this cockpit, need to descend.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}长耳大野兔 驾驶舱外有枪声 需要下降
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.22,1:27:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a negative, Flight 10, do not deviate from your current course or altitude.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 10次航班 不得改变目前航线及高度
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.47,1:27:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转身
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.35,1:27:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need all of you to put your hands\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们都把手
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.77,1:27:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the seat-back in front of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}放在前面的座位上
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.39,1:28:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}照做
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.27,1:28:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Move. - Don't test me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 走 - 别惹火了我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.82,1:28:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}后退
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.36,1:28:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands up!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把手抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.86,1:28:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.07,1:28:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit, sit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.32,1:28:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was supposed to be in the seat next to mine.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他本来是坐在我旁边的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.28,1:28:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He was close enough.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 但也不远
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.20,1:28:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, whatever I've done to you, whatever it is, I'm sorry.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听我说 不管我哪里对不起你 我表示道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.04,1:28:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}老实坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.38,1:28:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, I'm not mad at you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔 我不是生你的气
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.38,1:28:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my hero.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是我的偶像
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.88,1:28:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People everywhere are gonna remember the name Bill Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世界各处的人都将记得比尔·马克斯这个名字
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.68,1:28:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alcoholic, self-destructive,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个持有枪和警徽的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.80,1:28:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suicidal man with a gun and a federal badge\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}自暴自弃的酒鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.89,1:28:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who changed everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}改变了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.01,1:28:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think doing this is gonna change?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这样做又能改变什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.93,1:28:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two minutes outside the window. Suit up.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有两分钟 穿好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.19,1:28:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of these people boarded this plane\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每个上这个飞机的人
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.06,1:28:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believing their country would protect them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}相信国家能保护他们
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.86,1:28:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you would protect them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}相信你能保护他们
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.78,1:28:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"各位
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.24,1:28:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be okay!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"我们不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.32,1:28:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an air marshal on board.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机上有个空警"
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.58,1:28:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how easy this was?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道说这话有多么轻松吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.74,1:29:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I failed. You've made your point.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你说得对 我失败了 你证明了你的观点
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.25,1:29:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Bill, you failed miserably!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 比尔 你是惨败
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.79,1:29:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three thousand people died that day, including my father!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那天死了三千人 包括我父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.09,1:29:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I joined up 'cause I wanted to go fight the cowards that did it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}于是我参军 因为我想与恐怖分子作战
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.09,1:29:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just ended up fighting in a war that I still don't understand\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可我却参加了一场至今也无法理解的战争
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.34,1:29:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came home to a country where nothing had changed.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回国之后 这个国家也没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.85,1:29:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但今后不同了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.43,1:29:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security is this country's biggest lie.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}安保是这个国家最大的谎言
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.56,1:29:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our homes, in our cities, in our planes, no one's safe,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我们的家里 城市里 飞机上 没人是安全的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.61,1:29:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one day somebody worse than me is gonna expose that lie,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将来会有比我更狠的人揭露这一谎言
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.53,1:29:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the last thing our children will see\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们的后代最后看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.70,1:29:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is our failure as it destroys them.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就是我们的失败毁灭了他们
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.91,1:29:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Bill, you are that lie!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你 比尔 你就是这个谎言
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.45,1:29:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just have handed out pamphlets.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你散发传单就是了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.16,1:29:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been a lot easier.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那样简单得多
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.96,1:29:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change the world with words, Bill,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}言语是无法改变世界的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.80,1:29:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you write those words in the evening news with blood.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非是用鲜血写成的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.01,1:29:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们必须走了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.13,1:29:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're military. These are the people you fought to protect.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们是军人 他们是你们该保护的人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.68,1:29:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to protect my country, and that's what I'm doing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的誓言是保护国家 这也是我正在做的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.01,1:30:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You believe that? - I do.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 这话你信？- 我信
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.81,1:30:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also believe we'll be $150 million richer.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也相信我们会赚到1.5亿美元
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.60,1:30:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get that money. It's in an account in my name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们拿不到那笔钱 账户是在我的名下
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.15,1:30:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in a trust in your name.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是你名下的托管账户
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.15,1:30:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I die, the money moves.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一死 这钱就转移
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.15,1:30:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To 100 accounts, 27 countries,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转移到27个国家的100个账户
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.86,1:30:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each of those into 100 other accounts.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其中每个账户再转移到100个账户中
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.99,1:30:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think you're gonna jump?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们打算什么时候跳机？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.20,1:30:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35,000 feet? You'll be dead in four seconds.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在3.5万英尺高度 你们4秒内就会死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.33,1:30:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll jump when the pilot follows explosive protocol\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等飞行员启动爆炸预案 下降到8千英尺时
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.91,1:30:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and drops us down to 8,000 feet.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们就跳机
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.33,1:30:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you think of, we've thought of a thousand times.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你所能想到的 我们都考虑过无数次了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.08,1:30:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been instructed to shoot us down if we try to descend.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我们下降的话 他们有命令击落我们
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.67,1:30:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bullshit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.17,1:30:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna kill all these people.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们不会杀了这些人的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.21,1:30:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hijacked flight. We're a classified threat to ground.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是被劫持的客机 我们对地面有重大威胁
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.05,1:30:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't disarm that bomb, everyone on board will die, including you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不拆除炸弹的话 机上人人都会死 包括你们
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.22,1:30:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think of that?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们考虑到这一点了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.89,1:30:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Look, I'm prepared to die. - We're not gonna die.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我已准备好去死 - 我们不会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.19,1:30:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say again, Jackrabbit. I need to descend.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再说一遍 长耳大野兔 我需要下降
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.94,1:30:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a negative, Flight 10.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 10次航班
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.44,1:30:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stick with the plan. We descend, we jump.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们按原计划 下降 跳机
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.28,1:30:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane goes down, we have enough money.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}飞机坠毁 我们有足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.82,1:30:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do whatever we want.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想干什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.20,1:30:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it, Tommy. We can disappear and never come back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想想吧 汤姆 我们可以人间蒸发 再也不回来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.28,1:31:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me? Never be found, ever. Mission accomplished, right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你听见吗？没人找得到我们 永远 任务完成 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.33,1:31:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now we need to get the hell off this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但现在 我们要离开这架飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.37,1:31:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zack, you and I both know we were never getting off this plane.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}扎克 你也清楚我们是下不了这架飞机的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.21,1:31:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zack, whatever your name is, you don't have to die.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}扎克 不管你真名叫什么 你不必送死
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.26,1:31:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't save these people, save yourself.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就算你不愿救这些人 也救救自己
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.09,1:31:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disarm the bomb.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拆除炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.47,1:31:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, do it.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.82,1:31:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a martyr, like you and me, Bill.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是个殉道者 就像你我一样 比尔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.49,1:31:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroes don't need to be remembered or recognized.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真正的英雄不需要被人记住或承认
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.91,1:31:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroes do whatever's necessary.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真正的英雄做任何必要的事
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.96,1:31:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wouldn't understand.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看来我不会理解了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.75,1:31:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fuck it! - I guess you wouldn't.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 不管了 - 看来你不会
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.32,1:32:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.00,1:32:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20,000! Come on, you wanker!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}两万英尺 快点 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.90,1:32:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8,000 feet! Come on, come on!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}8千英尺 快 快
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.82,1:33:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比尔
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.09,1:33:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8,000!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}8千英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.86,1:33:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- AQ 10, climb back up to 25,000 feet! - There's a bomb on board!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 10次航班 爬回2.5万英尺 - 机上有炸弹
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.65,1:33:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get this plane on the ground.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我需要让飞机着陆
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.87,1:33:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nancy, move, move! Everybody down, heads down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南希 快走 大家都趴下 低头
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.66,1:33:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Bill!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂 比尔
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.37,1:33:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off this plane!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要下飞机
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.88,1:33:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in your way, asshole?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我挡了你的路？混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.78,1:34:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.90,1:34:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it quick! Heads down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快点 低头
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.70,1:34:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.50,1:34:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kyle! You can do this! You can do this, come on.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}加油 凯尔 你能行的 你能行的 加油
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.43,1:34:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,severe damage to your fuselage.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的机身严重受损
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.93,1:34:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to maintain control?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能保持控制吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.23,1:35:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.11,1:35:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuel dump in progress.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}燃油倾泻中
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.62,1:35:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Copy that, Flight 10. - Come on, damn it!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 收到 10次航班 - 加油 该死的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.20,1:35:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little longer, come on!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}距离再长一点 加油
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.22,1:35:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.81,1:35:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the belt! Get the belt!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}解开安全带 解开安全带
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.11,1:35:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hang on! - Bill, help me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 抓住 - 比尔 救救我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.07,1:35:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becca, I have you!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}贝嘉 我抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.78,1:35:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang onto me! Hang onto me!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抓紧我 抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.84,1:36:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay? Are you okay?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你还好吧？你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.76,1:36:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Door is disarmed. - Release your seatbelts!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 舱门已拆下 - 解开安全带
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.18,1:36:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take her. Everybody. - Come on with me.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 带她走 各位 - 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.85,1:36:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undo your seatbelt! Move to the front, quickly.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}解开安全带 到前面去 快
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.31,1:36:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything. Come this way, up to the front.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么也不要带 这里来 到前面去
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.40,1:36:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One at a time, please.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个一个来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.53,1:36:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么也不要带
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.45,1:36:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么也不要带
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.87,1:36:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to the front.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去前面
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.87,1:36:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么也不要带
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.70,1:37:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All passengers and crew accounted for.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有乘客和乘务人员都在这里了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.66,1:37:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, are you all right?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你呢 你怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.33,1:37:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a hell of a landing.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这次着陆真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.09,1:37:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than one hour ago, British Aqualantic Flight 10\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不到一小时前 英国亚奎兰蒂航空公司10次航班
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.38,1:37:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made an emergency landing after a bomb exploded mid-air.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在空中炸弹爆炸后 紧急迫降
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.76,1:37:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This following an attempted hijacking, yet in an unbelievable twist,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是发生在一起劫机未遂案之后 但情节极为曲折
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.76,1:37:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the suspected hijacker, U.S. Air Marshal Bill Marks,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}劫机嫌疑犯美国空警比尔·马克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.85,1:37:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turned out to be the hero.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}原来是英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.64,1:37:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Marks who confronted and killed the hijackers,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是马克斯对抗并杀死了劫机犯
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.06,1:37:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saving the lives...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拯救了…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.86,1:37:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah? - It's Marenick.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 喂 - 我是麦尼克
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.61,1:37:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to break protocol, Agent Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在轮到我违反规定了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.16,1:37:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling from my personal line\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我这是用私人线路打的电话
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.49,1:37:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll deny this conversation ever took place.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也会否认说过下面的话
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.95,1:38:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Bill, what you did on that plane, what you were up against,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听着 比尔 不管你在机上做了什么 面临了什么情况
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.21,1:38:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know I was wrong about you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想告诉你 我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.38,1:38:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll have my full support.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会全力维护你的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.71,1:38:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciate that.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.26,1:38:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Bill,\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}另外 比尔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.43,1:38:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna need that money back.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要收回那笔钱
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.81,1:38:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What money?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么钱？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.64,1:38:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Agent Marks.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保重 马克斯特工
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.12,1:38:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshal!\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}空警
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.16,1:38:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reilly, you son of a gun.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雷利 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.71,1:38:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, give me a loaded weapon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下次给我有子弹的枪
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.50,1:38:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, don't get shot.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下次要躲开子弹
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.67,1:38:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.34,1:38:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give you back your ribbon.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要把你的丝带还给你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.10,1:39:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it anymore.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不再需要它了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.52,1:39:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That-a-girl.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.85,1:39:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your dad.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你爸爸的电话
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.94,1:39:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.37,1:39:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, I was looking for you! - Hey.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 嘿 我正找你呢 - 嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.25,1:39:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you know where we are? - Iceland.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你知道这是哪里吗？- 冰岛
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.50,1:39:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Well, never been to Iceland.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哦 从没来过冰岛
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.01,1:39:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I've seen it, few times from plane windows, but...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是说 我在飞机上见过几次 不过…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.87,1:39:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.22,1:39:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.21,1:39:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stood by me, even after all that happened.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你一直站在我这边 不管发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.52,1:39:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.58,1:39:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good man.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.46,1:39:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your daughter would have been proud of you.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你女儿肯定也会为你自豪的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.23,1:39:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, ma'am.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 女士
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.49,1:40:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.92,1:40:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.53,1:40:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you headed?\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.16,1:40:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depends.\N{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看情况
